data.description: Welcome to 87465 Creekside Dr, Yulee, where modern elegance meets peaceful living. This stunning home offers contemporary design, open-concept layout, and abundant natural light, creating an inviting ambiance. Enjoy a gourmet kitchen, tranquil master suite, and smart home features. Step outside to an expansive outdoor area perfect for gatherings. Rest assured knowing that this property offers seclusion and privacy, allowing you to escape the hustle and bustle of daily life and enjoy your own piece of paradise. Screened Heated Jacuzzi Pool and over a half an acre of piece and quiet, HVAC was replaced a year ago, also has a home generator to keep you cool should the power go out. Inside has been freshly repainted, home is tight and right now., your will love this property.
